title: #57: Parenthoodwinked (with Joey Diaz)
itunes:title: Parenthoodwinked with Joey Diaz
description: Joey Diaz invited me over to his house to talk about the daughter he barely ever mentions. As always with Joey Diaz, some of these stories are amazing. He's so honest and colorful, I could just sit and listen to him for days.
